{"tid":1584684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣超進化] 由被動share轉為主動置入計畫","createTime":"2019-09-21T09:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T09:11:16.000Z","uid":264327,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8deabf1968a5bac0f8481a9a1bf376c35baa0b","tid":1584684,"uid":264327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"以前文宣都係整好圖靠大家share出去，但我發現咁樣好被動，唔知係咪真係有人share、share喺邊同反應係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我係度正式提出<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[文宣超進化] -主動置入計劃</span></strong></strong></span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以100%確保文宣有出到街，仲可以track到唔同數據，包括係邊度出、有幾多人睇同後續迴響etc.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我會諗到？<br />\n有日望到呢篇，覺得入面個B6真係太天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識得主動將香港時事置入落去個台灣forum度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1582281/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1582281/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣組要再分條line出黎，負責置入，我就覺得可以搵各地留學生做，負責置入各地forum<br />\n亞洲我諗台灣同韓國有得做，外國我就唔熟，大家再諗諗<br />\n<br />\n用台灣個case<br />\n上面條link個forum Dcard係for大學生，即係話係台灣讀書既香港人可以註冊，已經可以做置入。<br />\n我研究左一陣，發現原來香港人都可以註冊，仲要upload證件，加上又係台灣野，唔洗驚有狗註冊到<br />\n重點係入面有香港版，已經見到入面有巴絲打組團、傾野。仲有義守俾人打單野，都唔少人過左去推文，好多台灣人知。<br />\n<br />\n係既台灣人係關心香港，不過始終都未必跟得貼。如果我地不停留落熱門既文度，起碼有幾千人到幾萬人睇，個效應都幾大(再加埋有班係台灣既學生睇，又多左人知)<br />\n<br />\n真係覺得行得通喎 有無人有興趣一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n範例:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFvnwum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFvnwum.jpg&h=ebeed710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8F6X9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8F6X9n.jpg&h=94b9c641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ff2125c72f5f8ee1bd50ea47c7dfaf02e76ed81","tid":1584684,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"a0bcf6c280736df4e7072e9f88a7320cacf5faec","tid":1584684,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}